_sText:
zm_HellsDam

A fast round zombie mod map 

FEATURES

Two fully barricadable houses
A Tram (goes across the river)
breakable objects
High FPS
small and chellenging for both sides
quick download time for otheres

Story?  players start at the bottom of the dam and must work there way up to the top the valley to escape.
 
notes: i made this while working on my de_MW2_Terminal map. i needed a change and i wanted a dam in the map.
it did not take very long so there is a few silly bugs however it is a final so meh.



install: pput BSP in you map folder steam/steamapps/accountname/counterstrike-source/cstrike/maps
